          "Hero",
          "Features",
          "HowItWorks",
          "CTA"
        ],
        "content_notes": "Hero section with dark gradient background, animated text showing 'Learn ML with AI', call-to-action buttons for Sign Up and Login. Features section displaying 4 learning modalities with glassmorphism cards. How It Works with step-by-step process. CTA section encouraging sign-up.",
